item.title: Title: Humour Meets History: James Fell's Unique Take on the Past
item.description: Description: In this special episode of 'What She Said,' join me as I chat with James Fell, author of 'On This Day in History, Shit Went Down.' Together, we explore how his irreverent yet insightful approach to history brings a fresh perspective to events of the past. From his personal journey to his humorous and serious reflections on historical lessons, this episode is a delightful blend of laughter, learning, and the unexpected twists of history. item.title: ENCORE | The Fine Art Fugitive
item.description: ‘Tis the season for spending obscene amounts of money. That’s something superstar art dealer Inigo Philbrick excels at. In this re-run from last year, the art world hustler starts making big money “flipping” works of art. Before long, he’s selling shares of paintings to investors all over the globe, all while becoming known for his jet-setting and expensive taste. But when he makes too many promises he can’t keep, this art world svengali will lose it all. See Privacy Policy at https://art19... Feed: https://rss.art19.com/scamfluencers
